{"id": "1521760226557300797", "channel_id": "1521760226557300797", "author_id": "575594364781199361", "author_name": "mckaigne", "content": "大家好，\n\n我在浏览兑换商店时，由于粗心大意加上作为新玩家缺乏经验，我不小心在手机上用约 6000 点\"沉积物\"（sediment）兑换了大量\"悖论契约\"（Paradox Covenants）。这是一次误操作，我想知道是否可以进行数据回档，或者是否有相关渠道可以申请处理。兑换数量甚至超出了邮箱容量。我目前还没有使用或分解这些物品。\n\n事故发生时间：2026-07-01 09:03:42\n\n我平时在购买物品时非常谨慎，因为担心因经验不足而做出错误的投资决定，所以这次失误对我来说损失相当惨重……我也注意到另一位玩家在类似情况下获得了回档处理，希望能获得同等机会。\n\n这段文字是使用翻译工具生成的，如有不准确之处，敬请见谅。\n\nHello everyone,\n\nI went through the exchange shop and in a mix of carelessness and general lack of knowledge as a new player, I accidentally spent around 6000 sediment on Paradox Covenants on my phone. This was an accidental purchase and I was wondering if a rollback is possible or if I can apply for it somewhere. The quantity was so large it didn't even fully fit in my mailbox. I have not touched or dismantled any of the items.\n\nTime of incident: 2026-07-01 09:03:42\n\nI am very careful with purchases as my lack of knowledge makes me scared of making bad investment decisions, so this is quite the big hit for me. I am also aware another player had a similar situation rolled back, and I hope the same is possible here.", "timestamp": "2026-07-01T06:11:50.949000+00:00", "thread_id": "1521760226557300797"}
